{"tid":1822498,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"(Switch) 川島隆太教授 腦力鍛鍊 （原來有支筆送架）","createTime":"2020-01-13T04:11:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-13T04:48:07.000Z","uid":240448,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"bfd2312507be59b2bc813b8292325e9f94a9274a","tid":1822498,"uid":240448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T04:11:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fKSEVbk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfKSEVbk.jpg&h=dc0180de&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n產品介紹<br />\n遊戲版本： 日英<br />\n產品原名： 東北大学加齢医学研究所 川島隆太教授監修 脳を鍛える大人のNintendo Switchトレーニング<br />\n主機平台： NS<br />\n遊戲類型： PZG<br />\n遊戲字幕： 日文英文<br />\n建議零售價： JPY 3,828<br />\n發售日期：<br />\n2019-12-27<br />\n遊玩人數: 1~2 人<br />\n <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bLOwMh2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbLOwMh2.png&h=bc5e4b4f&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qW03CpJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqW03CpJ.jpg&h=cef56d88&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hhkvhpK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhhkvhpK.jpg&h=b7f925a8&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BMzPxX5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBMzPxX5.jpg&h=5832b9fb&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5f4gcX6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5f4gcX6.jpg&h=0ae513a5&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=6_jnLSUquR8&amp;feature=emb_title\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D6_jnLSUquR8%26feature%3Demb_title&d=EP%2BJfZZVzGvO4DQPpGaiyBlCv%2FutJLQSKuuf3SGwDjg%3D&h=fe42c4ca\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=6_jnLSUquR8&amp;feature=emb_title</a><br />\n日本紹介映像<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=xWV5kI_hOA0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DxWV5kI_hOA0&d=EP%2BJfZZVzGvO4DQPpGaiyBlCv%2FutJLQSKuuf3SGwDjg%3D&h=056fc2cd\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=xWV5kI_hOA0</a><br />\n《川島隆太教授監修 大人的 NS 腦力鍛鍊》你有自信大腦年齡跟你的年齡一樣嗎？<br />\n<br />\n[商品介紹]<br />\n <br />\n  根據官方介紹，本次的《腦力鍛鍊（以下簡稱腦鍛）》將收錄使用 Joy-Con 控制器的全新訓練，以及至今為止系列作當中讓人熟悉的多種訓練項目。<br />\n<br />\n用手指來腦鍛<br />\n將 Joy-Con 上的動態感測 IR 攝影機朝向手指，就能夠讀取手指的形狀。本作中搭載了活用這項功能，利用擺動手指來進行訓練與腦年齡檢測的全新項目。<br />\n<br />\n《東北大學加齡醫學研究所 川島隆太教授監修：大人的 Nintendo Switch 腦鍛煉》將於 12 月 27 日發售，實體版售價 3480 日元（約 1000 台幣），並附贈一支觸控筆，下載版售價 2680 日元（768台幣），雖然對某些人來說這些小測試都很簡單，甚至懷疑這種遊戲的必要，但是無疑的是這作品的確打開了對遊戲來說更廣大的幼年與老年市場，3DS 版甚至到 2011 年共賣出 1483 萬套，成為任天堂主機史上最佳銷售遊戲之一，絕對有它獨特的銷售優勢。"},{"pid":"f614291d76d5ba0fb840648b91e0d3ac2c74a18e","tid":1822498,"uid":240448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T04:17:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MGSp6mA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMGSp6mA.jpg&h=fb322871&s={SIZE}\" />呢支是送的！好重手 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8abN38h.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8abN38h.jpg&h=4b20cd00&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mKzsjGE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmKzsjGE.jpg&h=802b0e3b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n黃店加30蚊有 <br />\n靚 <br />\n輕手d"},{"pid":"02748f8ffd1ea9e0dd416d7cc1af5921492d7bd7","tid":1822498,"uid":240448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T04:30:15.000Z","msg":"有無巴絲買左喇？<br />\n期待緊 佢地出world championship online"},{"pid":"93c95607d8ff6ebb4725986708c91cc938dd46a0","tid":1822498,"uid":132580,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T04:31:59.000Z","msg":"有買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />想玩返以前嘅要答兩題之前嘅數嗰隻計數但佢好似無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.